A demo dataset of European museums, artists, artworks, and exhibitions. This hub shows how NeoWiki connects
entities across schemas, mirroring the cultural-heritage scenarios ECHOLOT and GLAM partners work with. The
data is curated for demonstration and is not authoritative.

